net.proteusframework.users.model

Class PrincipalGroup_Principal

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.users.model.PrincipalGroup_Principal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class PrincipalGroup_Principal
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Association entity for Principal and PrincipalGroup. A Principal is "in" a a group if and only if a record of this class exists in the database. Other packages will typically use PrincipalDAO methods to add, remove, and test for records of this class.
    Author:
    Jonathan Crosmer (jcrosmer@i2rd.com)
